12:09.770 --> 12:13.189
I don't have
another 500, so...

12:13.274 --> 12:15.692
Wait a second.
He might.

12:17.078 --> 12:18.811
I have another thousand
on me.

12:18.863 --> 12:20.196
How do you have
another thousand?

12:20.281 --> 12:21.314
From the weed.

12:21.365 --> 12:23.166
I told you,
I got rid of it.

12:23.251 --> 12:26.920
Now do you have this guy
or not?

12:26.987 --> 12:28.371
I got kings full of 2s.

12:28.456 --> 12:30.040
He's got no aces showing,

12:30.124 --> 12:32.825
and <i>Jesus Christ Superstar</i>
folded one on first street.

12:32.877 --> 12:33.993
The only way he beats me

12:34.045 --> 12:35.662
is with trip 3s or trip 4s
under there,

12:35.713 --> 12:37.464
and Limp Bizkit
folded two 3s,

12:37.515 --> 12:40.050
and Dickcheese over here
had a 4.

12:40.134 --> 12:42.519
So he's got a...

12:42.603 --> 12:43.853
- A straight.
- Straight.

12:43.938 --> 12:44.888
Or he's bluffing,

12:44.972 --> 12:46.139
but either way,
I got him.

12:46.190 --> 12:47.474
Hey, do you always get
your girlfriend's advice

12:47.525 --> 12:48.725
on everything?

12:48.809 --> 12:50.677
Oh, this guy.

12:50.728 --> 12:53.196
Well, let's raise
another 500.

12:53.281 --> 12:54.481
Hmm.

12:54.532 --> 12:57.067
Don't ask for more
unless you wanna lose it.

13:05.242 --> 13:06.192
Call.

13:06.243 --> 13:08.662
Full house.

13:12.249 --> 13:13.416
Four 4s, asshole.

13:13.501 --> 13:15.085
Whoa, wait.
Wait, that's not possible.

13:15.169 --> 13:16.202
He had--

13:16.253 --> 13:18.138
he's cheating.

13:20.508 --> 13:22.676
And what are you
gonna do about it?

13:22.727 --> 13:24.877
You're not gonna get away
with this.

13:24.929 --> 13:26.546
Well, I guess
your only option

13:26.597 --> 13:28.765
would be
to call the police.

13:28.849 --> 13:30.210
Of course,
I haven't been drinking,

13:30.217 --> 13:32.352
'cause, you know,
I'm underage, like you boys.

13:32.403 --> 13:33.353
You set us up.

13:33.404 --> 13:35.522
Yeah.

13:35.573 --> 13:37.190
See, I remember you.

13:37.241 --> 13:38.742
First week,
you come into class,

13:38.826 --> 13:40.893
Mr. "Oh, I got
the whole textbook memorized."

13:40.945 --> 13:42.529
Made the rest of us
look like chumps.

13:42.580 --> 13:44.280
No, you did that
all by yourself.

13:44.365 --> 13:45.665
Yeah, well,
I don't need a super brain

13:45.733 --> 13:47.283
to remember some guy who thinks
his shit don't stink.

13:47.368 --> 13:48.284
- Whoa, whoa, whoa, dude.
- Hey, back up.

13:48.369 --> 13:49.502
Now get the hell outta here

13:49.570 --> 13:52.255
before we put you
out of here.

14:04.029 --> 14:05.378
Congratulations Harvey.

14:05.673 --> 14:07.468
I had no idea
Jessica was planning this.

14:07.629 --> 14:08.946
What do you want, Stephen?

14:09.098 --> 14:11.232
I hear Cameron
got a witness.

14:11.316 --> 14:13.768
He did.
What do you want?

14:13.852 --> 14:15.019
I'm just checking to see

14:15.070 --> 14:16.270
if there's anything
I can do to help.

14:16.355 --> 14:18.722
There isn't.

14:18.774 --> 14:21.576
Cheers.

14:23.328 --> 14:24.362
What do you got?

14:24.429 --> 14:25.446
I couldn't find out

14:25.531 --> 14:27.081
where Cameron's
got his witness hidden,

14:27.166 --> 14:30.084
but I figured out
who it is.

14:32.371 --> 14:34.071
What?

14:34.123 --> 14:35.840
So now I know
why you wanted to meet me

14:35.907 --> 14:37.875
at the elevator.

14:37.926 --> 14:39.377
Pretty awesome.

14:39.428 --> 14:40.845
Yeah, it is.

14:40.912 --> 14:42.847
What are you gonna do
about Jessica?

14:42.914 --> 14:44.849
I don't know.

14:54.476 --> 14:56.644
Nothing ever changes
around here.

14:56.728 --> 14:59.197
It's good to see you too,
Harvey.

14:59.264 --> 15:02.567
Now what was so important
that you just had to see me?

15:02.618 --> 15:04.768
I wanna talk to you
about extending my time

15:04.820 --> 15:08.322
at the D.A.'s office.

15:08.407 --> 15:10.491
Come with me.

15:10.576 --> 15:13.377
Now what's Cameron Dennis
offering you?

15:13.445 --> 15:16.080
Why does he have
to be offering me something?

15:16.131 --> 15:19.834
Because he knows, if you wanna
keep someone in your house,

15:19.918 --> 15:22.803
offer them
a better room.

15:22.888 --> 15:25.139
Head litigator.

15:25.224 --> 15:27.642
Do you wanna stay there
because it's a step up

15:27.726 --> 15:30.761
or because you can see yourself
there in ten years?

15:30.812 --> 15:32.180
Why do you wanna know?

15:32.264 --> 15:34.599
Because I have a promotion
ready for you right here.

15:34.650 --> 15:36.300
What are you talking about?

15:36.351 --> 15:38.903
Daniel Hardman and I

15:38.970 --> 15:41.989
are taking Gordon, Schmidt,
and Van Dyke down.

15:42.074 --> 15:43.774
That's why we're up here.

15:43.825 --> 15:45.693
Did you think
we were gonna make out?

15:45.777 --> 15:48.079
Man can hope.

15:49.147 --> 15:50.364
What?

15:50.449 --> 15:52.833
Are you sure you wanna
take control in the night?

15:52.918 --> 15:54.835
Nighttime's
when they're sleeping.

15:54.920 --> 15:56.787
Telling them you're coming
shows them respect.

15:56.838 --> 15:59.123
Not telling them
shows them more.

15:59.174 --> 16:00.291
What about honor?

16:00.342 --> 16:03.261
Harvey, we're lawyers.

16:03.328 --> 16:06.514
We're not
in the honor business.

16:08.767 --> 16:10.218
What did I always tell you
when you were here?

16:10.302 --> 16:12.687
Don't judge a man till you've
walked a mile in his shoes.

16:12.771 --> 16:14.939
Well, if you're ever
in these babies,

16:15.006 --> 16:19.610
we'll see if you feel
the same way.

16:24.366 --> 16:25.846
It's a little early
for batting cages,

16:25.850 --> 16:26.867
don't you think?

16:26.952 --> 16:27.985
I'm not going
to the batting cages,

16:28.036 --> 16:29.019
and you know it.

16:29.071 --> 16:30.071
Trevor, let it go.

16:30.155 --> 16:31.706
I can't.
I need that money back.

16:31.790 --> 16:33.190
What did you do?

16:33.242 --> 16:35.626
I haven't paid
for the weed yet.

16:38.196 --> 16:40.364
You took a loan
from a drug dealer?

16:40.415 --> 16:41.699
It's called consignment.

16:41.750 --> 16:43.534
Did you ever learn about
free enterprise in Econ 1a?

16:43.585 --> 16:45.419
No, but I read about
not betting money I don't have

16:45.504 --> 16:46.587
in Econ 1a.

16:46.672 --> 16:48.389
You told me you had him,
smart guy.

16:48.473 --> 16:50.091
I did have him,
and you know I did.

16:50.175 --> 16:52.760
Well, I need
a thousand dollars by Monday,

16:52.844 --> 16:54.512
or Omar's gonna beat
the living shit outta me.

16:54.563 --> 16:56.597
Trevor,
him kicking your ass

16:56.682 --> 16:58.266
doesn't get him
his money any faster.

16:58.350 --> 16:59.550
He's not gonna
see it that way.

16:59.601 --> 17:01.769
Okay, then we will think
of something else.

17:01.853 --> 17:03.321
I've been thinking,

17:03.388 --> 17:05.439
and the only thing
I came up with

17:05.523 --> 17:06.574
you're not gonna like.

17:06.657 --> 17:08.058
Why do I
have to like it?

17:08.109 --> 17:11.695
Because I can't do it.

17:11.747 --> 17:12.747
I told you before,

17:12.830 --> 17:14.699
I'm not selling
any test answers.

17:14.750 --> 17:16.900
It's not any test.
It's the test you just aced.

17:16.952 --> 17:19.453
It's not out there yet.
Nobody has it.

17:19.538 --> 17:22.957
I can make us 1,000 bucks
in one shot.

17:23.040 --> 17:24.291
Tell me you haven't memorized

17:24.376 --> 17:28.378
every question
and every answer, Harvard boy.

17:28.430 --> 17:29.747
That's what this is about,
isn't it?

17:29.798 --> 17:31.766
So what if it is?

17:31.850 --> 17:32.883
Look, you're bolting,

17:32.934 --> 17:34.418
and you're using
your brain to do it.

17:34.469 --> 17:35.586
I'm just asking,

17:35.637 --> 17:38.422
before you go,
use it to help me.

17:39.941 --> 17:42.259
Please.

17:48.567 --> 17:49.734
What the hell is this?

17:49.785 --> 17:51.319
It's the paperwork
for the Mackenzie deal.

17:51.403 --> 17:52.570
Type it up
and get it out.

17:52.621 --> 17:54.538
No, that report was
supposed to be disclosed

17:54.606 --> 17:55.623
during discovery.

17:55.707 --> 17:57.291
If you type up
what I gave you,

17:57.376 --> 17:59.126
you'd know
I'm disclosing it now.

17:59.211 --> 18:01.445
No, you're sticking it
in there now

18:01.496 --> 18:02.830
as if it's always been there.

18:02.914 --> 18:04.632
It's called bluffing.

18:04.716 --> 18:06.334
Okay, it's what I do.

18:06.418 --> 18:07.918
That's how I got the confession
in the first place.

18:07.969 --> 18:10.304
It's called bullshit,
it's what bullshitters do,

18:10.389 --> 18:12.473
and it's how innocent people
sometimes end up in prison.

18:12.557 --> 18:14.225
- Watch yourself.
- Excuse me?

18:14.292 --> 18:16.093
That toxicology report
doesn't change the fact

18:16.144 --> 18:17.812
that those two assholes
killed that woman.

18:17.896 --> 18:19.263
And you being
an asshole to me

18:19.314 --> 18:21.015
doesn't change the fact
that you are breaking the law.

18:21.099 --> 18:22.516
I'm not breaking the law.

18:22.601 --> 18:24.018
I put the goddamn thing
in there.

18:24.102 --> 18:26.020
They can find it
if they can think to look.

18:26.104 --> 18:28.472
Harvey,
you are making a huge--

18:28.523 --> 18:30.641
That's enough!

18:30.692 --> 18:32.526
I'm here.
You're here.

18:32.611 --> 18:34.779
Do your job.

18:45.090 --> 18:47.091
We know you have a witness.

18:47.158 --> 18:48.542
Surprised it took you
that long.

18:48.627 --> 18:49.877
And we know who it is.

18:49.961 --> 18:52.380
The man from the video,
Colonel Mariga.

18:52.464 --> 18:53.997
I don't have any prizes,

18:54.049 --> 18:56.384
so you'll just have to accept
a pat on the back.

18:56.468 --> 18:58.709
That's okay, Tom Selleck,
I don't need a pat on the back.

18:58.720 --> 19:00.240
I just need to know
what bullshit story

19:00.272 --> 19:01.472
he's gonna tell in court.

19:01.523 --> 19:02.640
It's not bullshit.

19:02.691 --> 19:03.891
He's gonna say
that Ava Hessington

19:03.975 --> 19:05.309
paid him to kill
those people.

19:05.360 --> 19:06.560
We're getting access
to him.

19:06.645 --> 19:08.562
No, you're not,
because I'm gonna say

19:08.647 --> 19:10.114
if she finds out
where he is,

19:10.181 --> 19:11.982
what's to stop her
from killing him too?

19:12.033 --> 19:14.351
You're not gonna bribe him,
you're not gonna threaten him,

19:14.403 --> 19:15.820
and you're not gonna
talk him out of it,

19:15.871 --> 19:18.906
because you're not gonna see him
until he gets on the stand.

19:18.990 --> 19:20.825
But what I will do
is allow you

19:20.876 --> 19:22.576
to take an offer
to your client.

19:22.661 --> 19:24.412
15 years, no parole.

19:24.496 --> 19:25.880
You're bluffing.

19:25.964 --> 19:27.581
He's not gonna say she knew
about the murders,

19:27.666 --> 19:29.867
because she didn't.

19:29.918 --> 19:31.552
I'll tell you what.

19:31.636 --> 19:34.755
Ten years with parole.

19:34.840 --> 19:36.340
Ah, make it nine.

19:36.391 --> 19:39.376
After all,
we used to work together.

19:49.090 --> 19:50.937
- How'd it go?
- Don't.

19:51.502 --> 19:52.500
- Was she hot?

19:52.872 --> 19:54.416
I sold her a math test
for $1,000.

19:54.417 --> 19:55.667
I wasn't thinking
of whether she was hot or not.

19:55.752 --> 19:57.318
Okay, I get it,
so, like, an eight?

19:57.370 --> 19:59.154
No, a ten wouldn't even
do her justice.

19:59.205 --> 20:00.756
- So six.
- Mm, she's a four.

20:00.823 --> 20:03.008
But she paid me $1,000,
so I bumped her up to a ten.

20:03.092 --> 20:04.159
Got it.

20:04.210 --> 20:06.178
Thank you, Michael.
Came through.

20:06.262 --> 20:07.679
Not yet.

20:07.764 --> 20:09.181
I'm coming with you
to Omar's.

20:09.265 --> 20:10.532
No, no, no, no,
you can't.

20:10.600 --> 20:12.517
Yes, I can.

20:14.270 --> 20:16.054
What's going on?

20:16.139 --> 20:17.472
I owed him the money
yesterday.

20:17.523 --> 20:19.007
How could you not
tell me that?

20:19.058 --> 20:20.776
Because I couldn't make the
test thing happen until today.

20:20.843 --> 20:22.043
I didn't want you
freaking out.

20:22.061 --> 20:23.445
Well, I'm definitely
coming with you now,

20:23.512 --> 20:26.782
and the only way you can
stop me is with that bat.

20:28.117 --> 20:30.869
You wanted to see me?

20:30.953 --> 20:32.988
What the hell is this?

20:33.039 --> 20:34.706
- It's the Mackenzie file--
- I know what it is.

20:34.791 --> 20:37.025
What the hell did you put
in the fine print?

20:37.076 --> 20:38.493
You too?

20:38.544 --> 20:40.864
You're gonna give me shit about
not disclosing this report?

20:40.880 --> 20:41.997
Not disclosing it?

20:42.048 --> 20:43.999
You gave it to 'em
on a silver platter.

20:44.050 --> 20:46.084
I don't understand.
You want me to take it out?

20:46.169 --> 20:48.053
I don't want you to do shit.
I've already taken it out.

20:48.137 --> 20:49.754
And if I'd wanted it disclosed,

20:49.839 --> 20:51.556
I wouldn't have misfiled it
in the first place.

20:51.641 --> 20:52.674
You buried it?

20:52.725 --> 20:53.892
Damn right I did.

20:53.976 --> 20:56.311
Cameron, look,
I'm all for skirting the law,

20:56.378 --> 20:57.896
but this is
breaking the law.

20:57.980 --> 20:59.181
So was killing that woman,

20:59.232 --> 21:01.049
and I'm not gonna let
those two assholes walk

21:01.100 --> 21:04.052
because our eyewitness had
a few beers at the ball game.

21:04.103 --> 21:05.887
They won't walk. That's why
I put it in the fine print.

21:05.938 --> 21:07.739
You think you're the first guy
to have this idea?

21:07.824 --> 21:09.691
Nobody does it
because it doesn't work.

21:09.742 --> 21:11.193
Well, that's exactly
why it can work.

21:11.244 --> 21:12.828
They won't think
to look at it

21:12.895 --> 21:14.779
because nobody
has the balls to do it.

21:14.864 --> 21:16.397
And what if they do

21:16.449 --> 21:18.750
and these guys get out
and they murder your brother

21:18.835 --> 21:20.118
or your father
or your cousin?

21:20.203 --> 21:21.336
'Cause I'll tell you
right now,

21:21.403 --> 21:23.738
they're gonna
murder someone's.

21:23.789 --> 21:25.423
I don't feel comfortable
with this.

21:25.508 --> 21:27.209
I don't give a shit whether
you feel comfortable or not.

21:27.260 --> 21:28.877
This is my case.
We're not disclosing it.

21:28.928 --> 21:30.345
It's done.
Cameron-

21:30.412 --> 21:32.264
I told you this before.
Don't make me tell you again.

21:32.348 --> 21:33.932
I'm here.
You're here.

21:34.016 --> 21:36.268
Do your job.

21:41.474 --> 21:43.475
- Keep the change.
- I need to speak with you.

21:43.559 --> 21:45.310
Okay, let's talk
on the way up.

21:45.394 --> 21:47.095
No, I prefer
to speak out here.

21:47.146 --> 21:49.614
I know that Cameron's
offered Harvey a deal.

21:49.699 --> 21:51.399
All right, I'm not going
behind Harvey's back.

21:51.450 --> 21:53.068
I don't want you
to go behind his back.

21:53.119 --> 21:54.619
I want you to go
to his face.

21:54.704 --> 21:55.770
And do what?

21:55.821 --> 21:56.938
It wasn't a deal.
It was an insult.

21:56.989 --> 21:58.273
It was an opening.

21:58.324 --> 21:59.491
Now he wouldn't
have offered anything

21:59.575 --> 22:00.909
if he wasn't willing
to negotiate.

22:00.960 --> 22:03.078
Maybe we can get him
down to five years.

22:03.129 --> 22:04.296
That's exactly
what he wants,

22:04.380 --> 22:05.630
to put Ava
in a position

22:05.715 --> 22:07.448
where she has to choose
between five years and life.

22:07.500 --> 22:09.000
That's a better position
than she's in now.

22:09.085 --> 22:10.646
He wouldn't have offered
anything at all

22:10.720 --> 22:11.786
if he wasn't bluffing.

22:11.837 --> 22:13.138
We're not gonna fall
for that bluff.

22:13.222 --> 22:14.662
Well, then Harvey's
making a mistake.

22:14.790 --> 22:16.591
Then take it up
with Harvey.

22:16.658 --> 22:18.793
You know as well as I do
Harvey is not interested

22:18.844 --> 22:20.661
in anything I've got to say
at the moment.

22:20.713 --> 22:22.130
You think Harvey's
making this call

22:22.181 --> 22:23.998
because of what's going on
between you and Donna?

22:24.049 --> 22:26.351
- It's clouding his judgment.
- Not about this.

22:26.435 --> 22:28.002
Right now
Harvey cannot see reason

22:28.053 --> 22:29.304
with respect to Cameron.

22:29.355 --> 22:31.189
He can't hear reason
with respect to me.

22:31.273 --> 22:32.713
Now you have a chance
to convince him

22:32.725 --> 22:33.975
to make a deal, Mike.

22:34.026 --> 22:36.311
Put yourself
in Ava Hessington's shoes.

22:36.362 --> 22:38.947
Would you want that choice
or not?

22:43.702 --> 22:44.852
Okay, whatever happens,

22:44.904 --> 22:47.705
just be quiet
and be cool.

22:47.790 --> 22:49.824
Okay.

22:56.882 --> 22:57.832
Who this?

22:57.883 --> 23:00.034
My friend.

23:00.085 --> 23:02.053
Hi.

23:09.145 --> 23:11.229
Inside.

23:15.651 --> 23:18.937
Don't move.

23:19.021 --> 23:21.556
Where's Omar?

23:21.607 --> 23:22.890
That's Omar.

23:22.942 --> 23:24.392
How is that Omar?

23:24.443 --> 23:26.161
He's obsessed
with <i>The Wire.</i>

23:27.997 --> 23:29.564
Are you kidding me?
Come on.

23:29.615 --> 23:31.249
I'm telling you,
he's no joke.

23:31.333 --> 23:33.093
Yeah, well, I know
I'm supposed to be scared,

23:33.118 --> 23:34.235
but I'm really not.

23:34.286 --> 23:36.337
Don't touch anything.

23:36.405 --> 23:39.924
Now unless my calendar
is messed up,

23:40.009 --> 23:41.259
today be Monday.

23:41.343 --> 23:42.677
- Omar--
- Shut up!

23:42.744 --> 23:44.295
Okay, I'm trying to decide
why I shouldn't call

23:44.380 --> 23:45.964
a couple of hard,
pipe-hitting negroes

23:46.048 --> 23:47.182
to come and work on you

23:47.249 --> 23:49.083
with a pair of pliers
and a blowtorch.

23:50.719 --> 23:52.270
I'm--I'm sorry, Omar.

23:52.354 --> 23:53.721
I don't have a reason,

23:53.772 --> 23:56.307
but I think the word
you be looking for

23:56.392 --> 23:58.476
isn't "negro."

23:58.561 --> 23:59.978
If you're gonna quote
<i>Pulp Fiction,</i>

24:00.062 --> 24:01.980
at least have the balls
to quote <i>Pulp Fiction.</i>

24:02.064 --> 24:04.816
- Omar--
- Shh, shh, shh.

24:09.038 --> 24:10.488
You know what they call
a quarter pounder with cheese

24:10.573 --> 24:11.573
in France?

24:11.624 --> 24:15.793
A royale with cheese,
mother flecker.

24:15.878 --> 24:18.129
- I love this negro!
- Yeah.

24:18.214 --> 24:19.797
Trevor,
you're off the hook.

24:19.882 --> 24:21.616
Never again.

24:21.667 --> 24:23.968
This be for you.

24:24.053 --> 24:26.554
