38:13.123 --> 38:15.041
Change of plans.
I'm back today.

38:15.125 --> 38:18.628
Who's your girlfriend?

38:18.679 --> 38:20.513
Oh, I'm not his girlfriend.

38:20.597 --> 38:22.382
I'm his girl Friday.

38:22.466 --> 38:24.133
Associates
don't get secretaries.

38:24.184 --> 38:25.835
I'm not like
other associates,

38:25.886 --> 38:27.220
and she's not like
other secretaries.

38:27.304 --> 38:29.972
- Bullshit.
- Donna?

38:30.024 --> 38:31.691
Okay, listen, <i>Rain Man,</i>
you wear lifts in your shoes,

38:31.775 --> 38:33.359
you want braces,
but you don't have the balls,

38:33.444 --> 38:34.861
and you have a cat

38:34.945 --> 38:38.514
that you love
more than it loves you.

38:38.565 --> 38:40.483
- Good to see you, Louis.
- Mm.

38:40.534 --> 38:43.703
I need a day.

38:45.956 --> 38:46.873
You going down?

38:46.957 --> 38:49.208
All the way up, asshole.

38:49.293 --> 38:51.026
I'll take the ride.

38:55.883 --> 38:58.051
Hey.
Hey.

39:01.839 --> 39:03.589
What's that?

39:03.674 --> 39:05.207
This is my way
of showing you

39:05.259 --> 39:07.677
that no matter
what you choose,

39:07.728 --> 39:09.896
I support you.

39:09.980 --> 39:11.848
And if your dream
is to go to Stanford,

39:11.899 --> 39:14.901
then that's my dream
for you too.

39:21.892 --> 39:23.693
How does it look?

39:23.744 --> 39:26.696
I have to admit,
it looks pretty good.

39:28.532 --> 39:30.867
So what changed
your mind?

39:45.099 --> 39:46.382
You got into Harvard?

39:46.433 --> 39:48.851
It's a--
it's a long story,

39:48.919 --> 39:50.419
but I have to go
right now.

39:50.471 --> 39:53.639
I wanted to be here
when you got home.

39:53.724 --> 39:54.857
But if you let me,

39:54.925 --> 39:56.425
I'd like to come
straight back here

39:56.477 --> 39:57.727
and tell you
the whole thing.

39:57.778 --> 39:59.445
Okay.

39:59.530 --> 40:01.697
Okay.

40:10.865 --> 40:13.984
Any progress
getting to Mariga?

40:14.035 --> 40:15.298
Cameron's not just bluffing

40:15.299 --> 40:17.050
about what Mariga's
gonna say.

40:17.135 --> 40:18.135
He doesn't even have him.

40:18.136 --> 40:19.136
That means we--

40:19.187 --> 40:21.504
We win.
It's over.

40:23.474 --> 40:26.560
Ah, it's gonna be fun
telling Cameron that.

40:26.644 --> 40:28.028
It's gonna be fun for Mike.

40:28.112 --> 40:30.480
I've got
something else to do,

40:30.531 --> 40:32.816
and it's not
gonna be fun.

40:32.867 --> 40:34.735
Is that
why we're up here?

40:34.819 --> 40:36.686
You remember
when you told me you decided

40:36.738 --> 40:39.856
to take Gordon, Schmidt,
and Van Dyke down?

40:39.907 --> 40:42.125
I guess that is
why we're up here.

40:42.193 --> 40:43.577
You said,
take them in the night

40:43.661 --> 40:45.361
because nighttime's
when they're sleeping.

40:45.413 --> 40:46.713
And you thought
I was wrong.

40:46.798 --> 40:49.249
And then you said
if I were ever in your shoes,

40:49.333 --> 40:53.053
I might think differently.

40:53.137 --> 40:54.838
What'd you do, Harvey?

40:54.889 --> 40:57.207
I made a move
in the night.

40:59.060 --> 41:01.478
I get Ava Hessington
acquitted...

41:03.765 --> 41:05.548
Darby backs me
for managing partner.

41:15.743 --> 41:17.727
I guess congratulations
are in order.

41:17.779 --> 41:19.539
I'm here to tell you
I don't want it anymore.

41:19.580 --> 41:21.415
Get out of my sight.

41:44.055 --> 41:45.889
You look ready
to attack.

41:45.940 --> 41:48.058
Does Harvey know his puppy's
off his leash?

41:48.109 --> 41:49.926
Harvey said he didn't need
to waste a trip down here

41:49.977 --> 41:52.595
just for me to tell you
I have my eye on the ball.

41:52.647 --> 41:54.865
I'm afraid
I don't follow you.

41:54.932 --> 41:56.266
Mariga.

41:56.317 --> 41:58.201
You weren't lying
about what he would say.

41:58.269 --> 42:00.270
You were lying about having him
in the first place.

42:00.321 --> 42:02.041
This whole thing
was designed just to get us

42:02.106 --> 42:04.574
to sign your bullshit deal.

42:04.625 --> 42:05.709
You're right.

42:05.776 --> 42:07.377
We didn't have him,
but we do now,

42:07.444 --> 42:09.329
and he's on a flight
as we speak.

42:09.413 --> 42:11.581
So you do me a favor,
and you tell Harvey

42:11.632 --> 42:13.793
he can take that bullshit deal
and shove it up his ass,

42:13.835 --> 42:14.968
'cause we're going
to trial.

42:15.052 --> 42:16.136
No way.

42:16.220 --> 42:17.287
If you didn't have
Mariga yesterday,

42:17.338 --> 42:18.621
you don't have him today.

42:18.673 --> 42:21.141
Why don't you ask
your friend Stephen Huntley?

42:21.225 --> 42:24.261
He's the one who led me
right to him.

